rows.label: qst000105_msg001
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Phew. Looks like the Trent
Krabbles have given up.

rows.label: qst000105_msg002
rows.name: Let's go report back to Isolde-san.

rows.label: qst000105_msg003
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Phew. The Trent Krabbles
probably won't be back now.

rows.label: qst000105_msg004
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]Let's go back and report to Isolde-san.

rows.label: qst000105_msg005
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Phew~ Finally a break, mo.
Those were some persistent
Trent Krabbles, mo.

rows.label: qst000105_msg006
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Time to go back and report
to Isolde-san, mo!

rows.label: qst000105_msg007
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Was that the last of them?
The Trent Krabbles have been
repelled. Mission complete.

rows.label: qst000105_msg008
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Shall we return and
report to Isolde-san?

rows.label: qst000105_msg009
rows.name:
Alriiiight! It seems the tenacity
of Thunderbolt Zeke has triumphed
over that of the Trent Krabbles!

rows.label: qst000105_msg010
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Let's report to Isolde-san,
and make it snappy!
